      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, \"clear example of judicial overreach\"? that seems like a huge claim. aren't there legal scholars who argue that originalism is the only way to actually respect the text of the constitution? why do you say it's definitely overreach instead of just a specific way of reading the law?",
